@startuml US_2.2.3_SSD
autonumber

actor "Port Authority\nOfficer" as Officer
participant ":System" as System

== Register Dock ==
activate Officer
Officer -> System: Clica na secção "Docks"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta página com lista de docks e opção "Register Dock"
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Register Dock"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de registo de dock
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Introduz dados do dock (name, location, length, depth, maxDraft, allowedVesselTypes) e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Update Dock ==
Officer -> System: Seleciona dock da lista
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta detalhes do dock
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Clica em "Edit Dock"
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta formulário de edição preenchido
deactivate System
Officer -> System: Modifica dados do dock e submete
activate System
System --> Officer: devolve mensagem de sucesso ou erro
deactivate System

== Search Docks ==
Officer -> System: Introduz critérios de pesquisa (name, vesselType, location)
activate System
System --> Officer: Apresenta lista de docks filtrados
deactivate System
deactivate Officer

@enduml
